Package ginRummy

Class Summary
Card Card represents a playing card in a deck of cards
Deck Deck represents a standard deck of playing cards with all the cards you'd expect except jokers Deck is a special type of Pile which can be cut and shuffled
Game Game is the main class to simulate a Gin Rummy card game of up to 4 players.
Hand Hand represents a hand of Cards in a card game Hand is a special type of Pile which can be tested as a winning hand in Gin Rummy
Pile Pile is a class for representing a pile of Card objects.
